      "modified": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "THREAT-2026-SMISH-001: Netflix Smishing Campaign — neflixpagocuenta.net",
      "description": "Multi-brand smishing campaign operating from bulletproof ASN AS213441 (SLAYER GROUP LIMITED). Primary vector: SMS impersonating Netflix billing. Kit deploys 7-stage credential harvesting including real-time 3D Secure fraud. Infrastructure spans 64+ domains across Netflix, Carte Vitale, logistics, banking, and healthcare brands. Modular PHP kit with gate.php translation API enables rapid brand switching.",
