      "name": "karript6",
      "description": "Francophone threat actor operating multi-brand phishing/smishing campaigns from bulletproof infrastructure since at least April 2020. Probable first name 'Romain' (derived from email romaintrdbl@gmail.com). WHOIS registration address in Dresden, DE — assessed as likely false. EXIF metadata places operational timezone at UTC+3. Zero public footprint. Moderate-high sophistication with real-time 3D Secure fraud capability.",
