      "name": "AS213441 SLAYER GROUP LIMITED — Bulletproof Hosting",
      "description": "Dedicated bulletproof ASN registered 2025-02-10 via RIPE NCC. 4x /24 IPv4 prefixes (1,024 IPs), ~1,760 domains. Upstream: AS30823 aurologic GmbH (sole provider — single point of disruption). Server stack: nginx, PHP 8.3.30, Plesk, Linux. SSL via Let's Encrypt R12. Anti-bot: Cloudflare Turnstile.",
      "infrastructure_types": ["hosting-malware"],
      "first_seen": "2025-02-10T00:00:00.000Z",
      "last_seen": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z"
