      "name": "Multi-Stage Credential Harvesting",
      "description": "7-stage phishing flow harvesting Netflix credentials, PII (name, address, phone, DOB), credit card data (number, expiry, CVV), banking PIN, and OTP codes via fake gate.php forms.",
