      "created": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
      "modified": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Real-Time 3D Secure Fraud",
      "description": "Threat actor initiates a real financial transaction while victim is on the phishing page. Victim is socially engineered into approving the 3DS challenge in their banking app, believing it is a verification step. The charge executes immediately.",
      "external_references": [
        {
